<chapter xml:id="ch-VennSymmetric" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
<title>Symmetric Venn Diagrams</title>

<introduction>
<p>
The main focus in this chapter are Venn diagrams that have rotational symmetry in the plane.
There are general results for non-simple diagrams and results for small <m>n</m>
  when the diagram is simple.
In the final section we will consider diagrams embedded on the sphere.
</p>
</introduction>

